	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Writes to PRG-ROM often cause the written value to be used by the mapper, if one is present. PRG-ROM stays intact of course, being ROM and all.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
