		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />One could, in theory, have RAM mapped into $8000-$ffff, but in practice external RAM, if any, is usually mapped into $6000-$7fff.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


