		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Except, of course, for one well-known Japan-only mapper that has ROM at $E000-$FFFF that's identical in all games, RAM at $6000-$DFFF, and a rewritable magnetic medium.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
